2001-3258 (La. 10/14/02)

STATE ex rel. Edward W. LEE v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 2001-KH-3258. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Lee, Edward W.; — Plaintiff; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Orleans, Criminal District Court Div. C, No. 372-324; to the- Court of Appeal, Fourth Circuit, No. 2001-K-1718.

Denied. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.8; State ex rel. Glover v. State, 93-2330 (La.9/5/95), 660 So.2d 1189.
